    <h1>Systems Master - All Systems & Projects</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated">
        <strong>Version:</strong> 1.00 | 
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Centralized containerized list of all Comserv systems with current documentation and database projects
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
        <h3>📦 Systems Organization</h3>
        <p>This document provides a containerized overview of all identified systems in Comserv. Each system container includes links to documentation and dynamically pulls associated projects from the database.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- AI & PRODUCTIVITY SYSTEMS -->
    <div style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;">
        <h2>🤖 AI & Productivity Systems</h2>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 15px;">
            <!-- AI Chat System -->
            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #2196f3;">
                <h3>AI Chat System</h3>
                <p>Real-time AI-assisted documentation and code search with multi-model support.</p>
                <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    <a href="/Documentation/AI">📄 Documentation</a> | 
                    <a href="/Documentation/AiChatSystemMasterAudit">📋 Master Audit</a> | 
